WEBVTT

00:00:25.647 --> 00:00:30.137
all I'd ever known and worn
was my school uniform,

00:00:30.161 --> 00:00:33.378
which, in fact, I was pretty grateful for,

00:00:33.402 --> 00:00:35.524
because from quite a young age,

00:00:35.548 --> 00:00:38.442
I'd realized I was somewhat different.

00:00:38.885 --> 00:00:41.245
I'd never been one of the boys my age;

00:00:41.269 --> 00:00:42.771
terrible at sports,

00:00:42.795 --> 00:00:45.456
possibly the unmanliest little boy ever.

00:00:45.480 --> 00:00:46.568
(Laughter)

00:00:46.592 --> 00:00:48.258
I was bullied quite a bit.

00:00:49.408 --> 00:00:54.140
And so, I figured that to survive
I would be invisible,

00:00:54.164 --> 00:00:55.749
and the uniform helped me

00:00:56.532 --> 00:00:59.149
to seem no different from any other child.

00:00:59.173 --> 00:01:00.350
(Laughter)